---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { focusAreas, siteData } from '../data/site';

const posts = await getCollection('posts', ({ data }) => !data.draft);
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Zihao Han and the purpose of this site." currentPath="/about">
  <section class="border-b border-stone-400/15 pb-12 pt-6 lg:pt-10">
    <p class="section-kicker">About</p>
    <h1 class="mt-5 max-w-4xl font-serif text-[clamp(2.8rem,7vw,4.8rem)] leading-[0.95] tracking-[-0.04em] text-balance text-ink">
      Research-driven, systems-aware, writing-first.
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base leading-8 text-muted sm:text-lg">
      我是 {siteData.name}（{siteData.alias}）。这个站点主要收纳我在自动飞行系统、机器学习与工程工具链上的长期技术笔记，也记录我如何把零散的实验、教程和阅读理解整理成可以反复回看的体系化文档。
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="grid gap-8 py-14 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.25fr)_minmax(280px,0.75fr)]">
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <section class="surface-panel p-7 sm:p-8">
        <p class="section-kicker">Why this site exists</p>
        <div class="mt-5 space-y-5 text-base leading-8 text-muted">
          <p>
            旧站点最初是一个基于 Hexo 构建的博客。随着笔记逐渐积累，旧有主题与部署流程变得不再适用。这次重构的目标不仅是视觉更新，更是为了建立一个适合长期系统性思考与知识归档的数字工作台。
          </p>
          <p>
            因此，这里剔除了常见的博客小组件与视觉噪音，转而采用更内敛、严肃的研究主页范式。排版设计优先考虑学术感、文字的可读性、段落的呼吸感，以及长期可维护性。
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="surface-panel p-7 sm:p-8">
        <p class="section-kicker">Current themes</p>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
          {focusAreas.map((area) => (
            <div class="rounded-[1.2rem] border border-stone-300/70 bg-white/65 p-5">
              <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl tracking-[-0.02em] text-ink">{area.title}</h2>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-muted">{area.description}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="surface-panel p-7 sm:p-8">
        <p class="section-kicker">Working style</p>
        <div class="mt-5 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-[1.1rem] border border-stone-300/70 bg-white/60 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted">Read</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-muted">从论文、官方文档与实践经验里提炼出可复用的理解框架。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-[1.1rem] border border-stone-300/70 bg-white/60 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted">Build</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-muted">把抽象理解落到真实环境中，验证部署链路、配置细节与边界条件。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-[1.1rem] border border-stone-300/70 bg-white/60 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted">Record</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-muted">最终以可复查的笔记形式沉淀，优先保证未来的自己也能快速接续工作。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <aside class="space-y-6">
      <section class="surface-panel p-6">
        <p class="section-kicker">At a glance</p>
        <dl class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-muted">
          <div>
            <dt class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">Archive size</dt>
            <dd class="mt-1 font-serif text-3xl text-ink">{posts.length} notes</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">Writing language</dt>
            <dd class="mt-1">Primarily Chinese, with occasional English framing where it helps readability.</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">Contact</dt>
            <dd class="mt-1">
              <a class="research-link" href={`mailto:${siteData.email}`}>{siteData.email}</a>
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">Code</dt>
            <dd class="mt-1">
              <a class="research-link" href={siteData.github} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">{siteData.github}</a>
            </dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </section>

      <section class="surface-panel p-6">
        <p class="section-kicker">Editorial principles</p>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-muted">
          <li>Long-form notes over feed-style updates.</li>
          <li>Typography and reading experience over visual clutter.</li>
          <li>Real experiments and implementation details over generic summaries.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
